Symbol.Script_2D:
!! Table Tennis.gsm
pen gs_cont_pen
hotspot2 0, 0 hotspot2 -2.754/2, -1.525/2 hotspot2 2.754/2, -1.525/2 hotspot2 2.754/2, 1.525/2 hotspot2 -2.754/2, 1.525/2
DRAWINDEX 30 fill gs_fill_type poly2_b 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -2.754/2, -1.525/2, 1, 2.754/2, -1.525/2, 1, 2.754/2, 1.525/2, 1, -2.754/2, 1.525/2, 1 line2 0, -1.525/2, 0, 1.525/2
if iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE then line2 -2.754/2, 0, -0.05, 0 line2 0.05, 0, 2.754/2, 0 endif
if iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED then for x=1 to 2 if net=1 then nx=0.01 else nx=0 poly2_ 8, 1, -nx, -1.525/2+vv, 1, -2.754/2+vv, -1.525/2+vv, 1, -2.754/2+vv, -vv/2, 1, -0.05, -vv/2, 1, -0.05, vv/2, 1, -2.754/2+vv, vv/2, 1, -2.754/2+vv, 1.525/2-vv, 1, -nx, 1.525/2-vv, 1 rot2 180 next x del 2 !!!!2*rot2 180!!!! endif
if area then DRAWINDEX 20 PEN area_cont_pen hotspot2 -areaLength/2, -areaWidth/2 hotspot2 areaLength/2, -areaWidth/2 hotspot2 areaLength/2, areaWidth/2 hotspot2 -areaLength/2, areaWidth/2 fill gs_fill_type poly2_b 10, 1+2+4+64, area_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -areaLength/2, -areaWidth/2, 1, areaLength/2, -areaWidth/2, 1, areaLength/2, areaWidth/2, 1, -areaLength/2, areaWidth/2, 1, -areaLength/2, -areaWidth/2, -1,
-2.754/2, -1.525/2, 1, 2.754/2, -1.525/2, 1, 2.754/2, 1.525/2, 1, -2.754/2, 1.525/2, 1, -2.754/2, -1.525/2, -1 if wall=1 then poly2_ 4, 1+4, -areaLength/2+wv, -areaWidth/2+wv, 1, areaLength/2-wv, -areaWidth/2+wv, 1, areaLength/2-wv, areaWidth/2-wv, 1, -areaLength/2+wv, areaWidth/2-wv, 1 endif else ! Minimal space DRAWINDEX 10 add2 -a/2, -b/2 call "fa_minimalspace" parameters A = A, B = B, MSFront = (areaWidth-B)/2, MSSide = (areaLength-A)/2, MSRear = (areaWidth-B)/2, MSType = 5, unID = 3000 del 1 endif
if net then pen gs_cont_pen DRAWINDEX 40 for x=1 to 2 add2 0, -1.525/2 fill gs_fill_type poly2_b 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -0.01, -0.12, 1, 0.01, -0.12, 1, 0.01, 0.06, 1, -0.01, 0.06, 1 line2 -0.01, 0.05, 0.01, 0.05 line2 0, 0, 0, -0.095 circle2 0, -0.1, 0.005 del 1 !!!!add2!!!! rot2 180 next x del 2 !!!!2*rot2!!!! endif
Symbol.Script_1D:
EPS = 0.0001
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2 DLEV3D_DRAFT = 3
! const values for parameter: iDet2D DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE = 1 DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED = 2
!! Table Tennis.gsm
vv=0.02 wv=0.025
!!!define texture "brick" "halo", 1, 1, 256+128, 0
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
!Hide all parameters from UI hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.` values{2} "iDet2D" DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED, `Детальный` VALUES "gs_resol" RANGE [3,)
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=7 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=91 if area_fill_pen=0 then parameters area_fill_pen=91
if area=0 then parameters a=2.754 parameters b=1.525 parameters ZZYZX=0.79 else parameters a=12.2 parameters b=6.1 parameters ZZYZX=1 ENDIF
lock "a" lock "b" lock "ZZYZX"
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then lock "net","netmat" endif
if net=0 then lock "netmat" hideparameter "netmat" endif
if area=0 then lock "wall","wallmat","areamat","area_cont_pen","area_fill_pen" hideparameter "wall","wallmat","areamat","area_cont_pen","area_fill_pen" endif
if wall=0 then lock "wallmat" hideparameter "wallmat" endif
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol" IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol", "gs_shadow"
Symbol.Script_UI:
! ============================================================================= ! Tabpage Structure Definition ! ============================================================================= TABID_Root =-1 _idxTab = 1 TABID_DimensionsAndMinSpace = _idxTab : _idxTab = _idxTab + 1 TABID_RepresentationAndSurfaces = _idxTab : _idxTab = _idxTab + 1 TABID_Descriptions = _idxTab : _idxTab = _idxTab + 1
! ============================================================================= ! Display actual tabpages ! ============================================================================= ui_dialog `Параметры Теннисного Стола` ui_current_page gs_ui_current_page
UI_PAGE TABID_DimensionsAndMinSpace, TABID_Root, `Размеры и Минимальное Пространство`, "uiTab_Dimension_flat(1)" gosub "DimensionsAndMinSpacePage"
UI_PAGE TABID_RepresentationAndSurfaces, TABID_Root, `Отображение и Покрытия`, "uiTab_2DRepr_flat(1)" gosub "RepresentationAndSurfacesPage"
UI_PAGE TABID_Descriptions, TABID_Root, `Характеристики`, "uiTab_Descriptions_flat(1)" gosub "Descriptionspage"
! -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Image links for archive ! -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- file_dependence "uiTab_Dimension_flat(1)" file_dependence "uiTab_2DRepr_flat(1)" file_dependence "uiTab_Descriptions_flat(1)"
! ============================================================================== end ! ==============================================================================
! ============================================================================== !Subroutines ! ==============================================================================
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "DimensionsAndMinSpacePage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ ! Sizes and Positions pageStartY = 2 yCurr = pageStartY diffY = 24
inFldWdt = 90 boolWdt = 220
inFldHgt = 19
xPos1 = 2
picWdt = 217 picHgt = 122
picPosX = 118 picPosY = 118 ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ui_style 0, 0
ui_infield{3} "net", xPos1, yCurr, boolWdt, inFldHgt, 7, "", 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, "", `Сетка`, 0, "", `Сетка`, 1
yCurr = yCurr + diffY
ui_infield{3} "area", xPos1, yCurr, boolWdt, inFldHgt, 7, "", 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, "", `Площадка`, 0, "", `Площадка`, 1
yCurr = yCurr + diffY
ui_infield{3} "wall", xPos1, yCurr, boolWdt, inFldHgt, 7, "", 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, "", `Ограждение`, 0, "", `Ограждение`, 1
yCurr = yCurr + diffY
! -------------------------------------------------------------------------- ui_separator xPos1, yCurr, 442, yCurr
! --------------------------------------------------------------------------
ui_pict 1 + area, picPosX, picPosY, picWdt, picHgt, 1
ui_infield{3} "areaLength", picPosX + 63, picPosY - inFldHgt - 2, inFldWdt, inFldHgt ui_tooltip `Длина Игровой Площадки` ui_infield{3} "areaWidth", picPosX + picWdt + 2, picPosY + 46, inFldWdt, inFldHgt ui_tooltip `Ширина Игровой Площадки`
return
